product.name: 3-Pack Fax Rattan Pendant Light Fixture Mini Hand-Woven White Rattan Chandelier 10.24" Boho Wicker Hanging Lamp for Dining Living Bedroom Kitchen Farmhouse
product.description:
Teru Ji Kaikang take your home from ordinary to extraordinary - whether that home is a Bohemian loft, modern farmhouse, or classic mid-century ranch.
White fax rattan+natural rattan craft, the pendants are made of 100% natural rattan and faux rattan materials. The lights are hand woven with by rattan craft superb skills rattan artists. Decorated with classic tropical style elements, creates a wonderfully new look.
Mini rattan pendant light, size: 26*29cm/10.24*11.42", Voltage: 110v~240v, Bulb socket and electric cord have passed the UL listed, which can ensure that you use them safely. US standard E26 base socket, maximum 60W, suitable for Incandescent, LED, Halogen, CFL, etc.(Bulb Not included).
Hardwired connection, durable and adjustable black cable (1.8m long/70.87") included. You can easily adjust the lenght of light cord to fit your room lighting needs. Suitable for different types of living rooms, restaurants, kitchens, dining rooms, laundry rooms, hallways, cafes, basements,corridor, stairwells,bars, clubs, libraries, office, entrance, bedrooms,reading rooms and more.
1. Natural Materials
Our products are made of high-quality bamboo, rattan, and straw rope.
Since these materials are natural materials, the following conditions may exist: bamboo knots, tiny burrs, slight color differences, micro scars, etc.
2. Handmade Products
Bamboo woven lamps are purely handmade, and there will be traces of handcrafting on the lamps in detail. Each product will have some differences, such as the following:
For example, if the interface of the bamboo lampshade ring is slightly larger or the gap is slightly different, it is not a quality problem. If you cannot accept the characteristics of natural materials and handmade products, please purchase with caution, we apologize for the inconvenience.
3.During the use of lamps, the color will change slightly over time, which is a natural change.
4. Please do not place the lamp in a location that is humid, cold or exposed to sunlight for a long time.
5. Routine Maintenance
Blowing: Prepare a hair dryer, clean around the product, and use the hair dryer to take care of some areas that are difficult to clean.
Wiping: Prepare a soft cotton towel, wring it out with water (do not rinse it directly with water) and gently wipe the surface of the bamboo product (do not use any detergent or corrosive chemical reagents to wipe the lamp).
You can also combine two cleaning methods to wipe the lamp at the same time. Just wipe the surface of the lamp with a wet cotton cloth that has been wrung out. And you can use a hair dryer to clean the hard-to-clean areas!
